thread.title: Judy

author: Judy
title: Judy
text:
The only thing I would improve on is putting a little more in the description area to make matching up parts a little easier. Example Cleveland steamer has several timer on the unit but if no description on if it is a minute cook timer or a holding timer and this might be a bad example but I think you should be able to get what I am saying. On the other hand it is AWESOME that I can turn the part around and look at all sides of the part before I order it.
Thank You
